data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Motivated Seller!!! GREAT FIND IN HIGHLY DESIRABLE BRENTWOOD HILLS! Enjoy coming home to your spacious 4 bedroom, 3 baths Pool home with excellent curb appeal. This three way split floorplan is ideal for privacy with the generous sized main living space accessible to all bedrooms. Inside your home you will find a separate living, dining and family room, a grand Master Bedroom Suite with garden tub, separate shower stall and dual vanities. Both the living and family room overlook the peaceful family pool and screened lanai area, which makes Florida indoor/outdoor living so much fun! The AC was replaced in 2014 with added dual bulb U/V system in the AC for air purification. The roof was replaced in 2017! Brentwood Hills is a great community with Community Pool, Tennis Courts, Basketball Court, Dog Park, Playground and Clubhouse! NO CDD fees! You are located close to shopping, schools, restaurants and golf courses! Come see this home today
